font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Menlo Regular\';\">✝</span></sup></td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: dotted windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">4 656</p></td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: dotted windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">5,2</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-bottom: dotted windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"70%\">Placer, saisir, déplacer de façon répétée des objets, sauf outils</td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: dotted windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">1 703</p></td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: dotted windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">1,9</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-bottom: dotted windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"70%\">Réaction du corps et effort, n.c.a.*</td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: dotted windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">11 367</p></td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: dotted windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">12,7</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"70%\">Réaction du corps et effort, n.p.<sup><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Menlo Regular\';\">✝</span></sup></td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">2 949</p></td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">3,3</p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-lastrow: yes;\"><td style=\"border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"70%\">Total</td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">89 539</p></td><td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"15%\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"right\">100,0</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt;\">* Non classé ailleurs</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><sup><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Menlo Regular\'; color: black; mso-fareast-language: FR-CA;\">✝ </span></sup><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-fareast-language: FR-CA;\">Non précisé</span></p><p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"À NOTER\" background_color=\"#7EBEC5\" use_background_color=\"on\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"center\" title=\"À NOTER\"]</p><p>Selon une étude de Lortie (2012), les systèmes de classification utilisés pourraient biaiser les statistiques sur les genres d’accident. L’expression « effort excessif » est abondamment utilisée comme genre d’accident. Il est possible que ce soit au détriment de l’« effort soudain », dont certaines causes sont sous-estimées, notamment les pertes d’équilibre.</p><p>Source: Lortie, M., (2012). Analysis of the circumstances of accidents and impact of transformations on the accidents in a beverage delivery company. <i>Safety </i><em>Science</em> 50, 1792-1800.</p><p>[/et_pb_cta][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"top\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\"]</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em;\">Source des statistiques de cette section : <em>CSST, Dépôt de données central et régional [DDCR]</em>, mise à jour 2011. Traitement : IRSST, 2013.</span></p><p>[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_sidebar admin_label=\"Sidebar\" orientation=\"left\" area=\"sidebar-1\" background_layout=\"light\" remove_border=\"off\"] [/et_pb_sidebar][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]</p>','Statistiques','','inherit','closed','closed','','163-autosave-v1','','','2016-09-23 20:46:31','2016-09-23 19:46:31','',163,'http://manutention.irsst.qc.ca/nouvelles/163-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1090,6,'2016-09-23 20:46:34','2016-09-23 19:46:34','<p>[et_pb_section admin_label=\"section\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\"][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Qu’est-ce que la manutention ?\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]</p><h1><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-292\" src=\"http://manutention.irsst.qc.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/logo-manutention-h1.png\" alt=\"logo-manutention-h1\" width=\"24\" height=\"30\" />Statistiques</h1><p>Les statistiques qui suivent précisent quels sont les travailleurs touchés par des troubles musculosquelettiques (TMS) associés à la manutention manuelle, les sièges et la nature des lésions, ainsi que leur origine.</p><p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_testimonial admin_label=\"LE SAVIEZ-VOUS ?\" url_new_window=\"off\"]</p><h3>LE SAVIEZ-VOUS ?</h3><h4><e